\"year\":\"2020\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-251\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-simply-retail-300x139.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022164\\u0022 height=\\u002276\\u0022 /\\u003e \\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-245\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-home-depot-300x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u002272\\u0022 height=\\u002272\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eLaunched Simply Green Retail Services with Home Depot.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eNamed Best Business of the Year (+100 employees) by the CanadianSME National Business Awards.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWere proud to have been ranked as Great Place To Work, 5 years in a row.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone size-medium wp-image-1011\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/logo-CanadianSME-Award-300x125.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022Simply Green has been named Best Business of the Year (+100 employees)\\u0022 width=\\u0022300\\u0022 height=\\u0022125\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-1027\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022Great Place to Work\\u0022 width=\\u0022147\\u0022 height=\\u0022148\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Raises Over $20,000 for Mental Health Initiatives\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWith support and contributions from our leadership, employees, and partners, Simply Group was able to raise $22,000 in just 19 days for Jack.org. All of the money was put toward helping 40,000 young people across Canada access vital mental health education and resources.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1147,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/press_release/simply-group-raises-over-20000-for-mental-health-initiatives/\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green has been named Best Business of the Year (+100 employees)\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThis honour was announced at an event hosted by CanadianSME Business Magazine in partnership with Cisco, Lenovo, and RBC, and is recognition of Simply Greens rapid assent to the ranks of Canadas most successful and leading companies.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1011,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 400px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-url\":\"/press-release/simply-green-has-been-named-best-business-of-the-year-100-employees/\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces in Canada\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eOur employees have always been our biggest asset, so providing them with a positive, inclusive, fun and rewarding work environment is a priority for us. Each year, we strive to build a company culture that empowers and inspires performance. Our goal is to deliver the best possible employee experience, and, to make that happen, we are continuously looking for ways to raise the bar, said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of Simply Group.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1027,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 250px;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/press_release/simply-green-recognized-as-one-of-the-best-workplaces-in-canada/\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes Acquisition of Dealnet in Transaction Valued at over $243 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022The Dealnet acquisition is highly strategic, and complementary to our business. With Dealnet on board we have further cemented our competitive advantage in the home improvement financing space. Our unprecedented dealer network will have access to a best-in-class suite of financing products and a significantly improved digital application experience,\\u0022 said\\u003cspan class=\\u0022xn-person\\u0022\\u003eLawrence Krimker\\u003c/span\\u003e, Founder and CEO of Simply Group. \\u0022No other Canadian home financing company can offer comparable opportunities to its dealers. We will continually look for new ways to enhance our dealer programs and bolster the value we offer them.\\u0022\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":847,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-dealnet-in-transaction-valued-at-over-243-million-808176167.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Acquisition Corp. Acquires 93.13% of Dealnet Capital Corp. and Commences Compulsory Acquisition\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWith the acquisition of Dealnet well on its way towards successful completion, I would like to thank Dealnets valued shareholders, employees and partners for their overwhelming support, said Brent Houlden, Dealnet Chief Executive Officer. Were delighted that our strategic review process resulted in a premium offer for shareholders and believe that we have found an ideal owner for the business in Simply Group and industry veteran Lawrence Krimker.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1064,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-dealnet-in-transaction-valued-at-over-243-million-808176167.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Dealnet and Simply Group Acquisition Corp. Announce Successful Take-up of Shares under the Offer\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWe would like to thank all of the Dealnet shareholders who have already taken advantage of this opportunity to realize the immediate value and tendered their shares. We are pleased to have taken up over 74% of Dealnets shares, said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of The Simply Group.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1058,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/10/15/2109099/0/en/Dealnet-and-Simply-Group-Acquisition-Corp-Announce-Successful-Take-up-of-Shares-under-the-Offer.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes Acquisition of Snap Financial Group in a Transaction Valued at $511 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022SNAP Financial Group\'s strong portfolio and extensive dealer network unlocks immediate scale-efficiency and value for Simply Group, providing us with a distinct market advantage that we will leverage to deliver extraordinary growth in both assets under management and shareholder value,\\u0022 said\\u003cspan class=\\u0022xn-person\\u0022\\u003eLawrence Krimker\\u003c/span\\u003e, Founder and CEO of Simply Group. \\u0022The combined strengths of Simply Group and SNAP will enable us to continue to drive innovation across a much-broader customer base with industry-changing products and services.\\u0022\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1066,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-snap-financial-group-in-a-transaction-valued-at-511-million-885985213.html\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes $71 Million Acquisition of Home Capital Groups Point-of-Sale Retail Lending Portfolio\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThe sale is aligned with Home Capitals strategy to exit non-core activities, while Simply Group looks to further fuel its growth in the consumer finance business by diversifying its product and consumer lending offerings beyond home energy solutions to home improvement generally.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1057,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20200903005822/en/\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"VersaBank Adds Simply Group Financial as Point-of-Sale Partner With Initial Financing of $72 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWe are thrilled to welcome Simply Group Financial as a new Point-of-Sale Financing partner, said David Taylor, President and CEO, VersaBank. Its a great time to be joining forces with Simply Group Financial with the home improvement industry experiencing a boom as Canadians spend more of their discretionary income on home renovations and upgrades amidst the pandemic. VersaBanks Point-of-Sale Financing business has been the primary driver of the significant expansion of our lending portfolio for the last eight years and we see this partnership as a tremendous opportunity for both organizations to execute on their growth strategies.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1065,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20200908005292/en/VersaBank-Adds-Simply-Group-Financial-Point-of-Sale-Partner\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green Home Services To Make Friendly, Premium All-Cash Offer to Acquire Dealnet\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022Simply Green has invested strategically to become a leader in the home comfort and home energy solutions sector, and this deal represents the next step in our continued growth. We are pleased this transaction will be adding over $200 million of finance receivables to our growing business, said Lawrence Krimker, Chief Executive Officer of Simply Group. With Simply Greens expansive and growing product offerings, and Dealnets underlying strength, we believe this acquisition will benefit our customers and investors and positions us well for the future. We look forward to commencing the tender process as soon as possible.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1051,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/10/27/2114761/0/en/Simply-Group-Acquisition-Corp-Acquires-93-13-of-Dealnet-Capital-Corp-and-Commences-Compulsory-Acquisition.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Investors', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'investors', '', '', '2021-03-10 15:58:36', '