(268, 1, '2020-07-16 06:13:29', '2020-07-16 06:13:29', 'Simply Green Home Services has been ranked in the Best Place to Work list for the fifth straight year in 2020. Significantly, this is our first-year ranking in the new 100-999 employee category, where we ranked 37th across all of Canada. We are proud to be recognized for our amazing culture, mainly because this recognition is based on feedback from our employees! We work tirelessly to develop programs and growth opportunities for our team. This achievement is proof that as we continue to grow and prosper, we continue to maintain and foster the family-style qualities that have made this such a great place to work.\r\n\r\nOur employees have always been our biggest asset, so providing them with a positive, inclusive, fun and rewarding work environment is a priority for us. Each year, we strive to build a company culture that empowers and inspires performance. Our goal is to deliver the best possible employee experience, and, to make that happen, we are continuously looking for ways to raise the bar, said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of Simply Group.\r\n\r\nAbout Simply Green Home Services\r\nSimply Green is one of Canadas leading residential and commercial energy services companies, with over 150 team-members and licensed contractors delivering energy-efficient solutions to over 160,000 happy clients across Canada. Simply Green was founded on the core premise of helping Canadians increase their homes energy efficiency without sacrificing their quality of life, resulting in reduced energy consumption, cost savings and an improved home environment.\r\n\r\nAbout Great Place to Work: Great Place to Work (www.greatplacetowork.ca) is the global authority on high-trust, high-performance workplace cultures. Through proprietary assessment tools, advisory services, and certification programs, Great Place to Work recognizes the Best Workplaces across the world in a series of national lists, including those published by Fortune magazine (USA) and The Globe &amp; Mail (Canada). Great Place to Work provides the benchmarks, framework, and expertise needed to create, sustain, and recognize outstanding workplace cultures.', 'Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces in Canada', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'simply-green-recognized-as-one-of-the-best-workplaces-in-canada', '', '', '2020-10-23 16:27:53', '2020-10-23 16:27:53', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=press_release&#038;p=268', 0, 'press_release', '', 0),
(269, 1, '2020-07-17 02:45:38', '2020-07-17 02:45:38', 'Four consecutive years of recognition including 4th place award for 2018 TORONTO, May 15, 2019 /CNW Telbec/ - Simply Green Home Services Inc., one of Canada\'s leading industry specialists in energy efficient home comfort solutions, is proud to announce that it has been recognized as the 4th best place to work in Canada by Great Place to Work<sup></sup> in the less than 100 employees category.\n<blockquote>\"We are deeply honoured to be recognized as one of the top five Best Workplaces in Canada this year,\" said Lawrence Krimker, CEO, Simply Group and Simply Green Home Services. \"Our employees have always been our biggest asset so providing them with a positive, inclusive, fun and rewarding work environment is a priority for us. Each year, we strive to build a company culture that empowers and inspires performance. Our goal is to deliver the best possible employee experience and, to make that happen, we are continuously looking for ways to raise the bar.\"</blockquote>\nThis is the 4th consecutive year Simply Green has been included in the list of nominees. Since it was founded in 2013, the company has consistently moved up the rankings rising from 42nd in 2015 to 25th in 2016 and 13th in 2017. This year, Simply Green is delighted that it was also nominated as one of the Best Workplaces for Women and Best Workplaces in Retail and Hospitality. About Simply Green Home Services Simply Green is one of Canada\'s leading residential and commercial energy services companies, with over 200 team-members and licensed contractors delivering ever-greener energy solutions to over 100,000 happy clients. Simply Green combines an HVAC servicing business. Simply Green was founded on the core premise of helping Canadians increase their home\'s energy efficiency without sacrificing their quality of life, resulting in reduced energy consumption, cost savings and an improved home environment.\n\nAbout Great Place to Work: Great Place to Work<sup></sup> (www.greatplacetowork.ca) is the global authority on high-trust, high-performance workplace cultures. Through proprietary assessment tools, advisory services, and certification programs, Great Place to Work recognizes the Best Workplaces across the world in a series of national lists including those published by Fortune magazine (USA) and The Globe &amp; Mail (Canada). Great Place to Work provides the benchmarks, framework, and expertise needed to create, sustain, and recognize outstanding workplace cultures.', 'Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces in Canada', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '268-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-07-17 02:45:38', '2020-07-17 02:45:38', '', 268, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/268-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
