(310, 1, '2020-07-17 04:34:23', '2020-07-17 04:34:23', 'A high-quality yet affordable option, the Goodman Furnace offers a quiet airflow system that automatically adjusts to heating demand so youre naturally comfortable. It works with both one- and two-stage thermostats, with provisions for a humidifier and electronic air cleaner.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Energy-efficient, multi-speed</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavy-duty, aluminized-steel tubular heat exchanger</li>\r\n 	<li>Stainless-steel secondary heat exchanger</li>\r\n 	<li>Two-stage gas valve provides quiet, economical heating</li>\r\n 	<li>Durable Silicon Nitride igniter</li>\r\n 	<li>Quiet two-speed induced draft blower</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple BTUs', 'Goodman Furnace', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'goodman-furnace', '', '', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=310', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(311, 1, '2020-07-17 04:36:10', '2020-07-17 04:36:10', 'A trusted name in heating for over 100 years, Lennox offers the EL296E that heats at two different intensities, all in the name of striking the perfect balance of comfort and energy. It even enhances your comfort during the summertime  by operating a lower speed, it reduces moisture levels inside your home.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Two-stage variable speed helps find a balance between energy use and comfortable warmth</li>\r\n 	<li>196 AFUE uses 2/3 less energy than a standard motor  96% efficiency</li>\r\n 	<li>Saving energy means you save money on your monthly bills</li>\r\n 	<li>High efficiency helps reduce your carbon footprint</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple BTUs', 'Lennox Furnace EL296E', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lennox-furnace-2', '', '', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=311', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(312, 1, '2020-07-17 04:38:03', '2020-07-17 04:38:03', 'Get consistent temperatures with two-stage heating to fine-tune your comfort at home and your energy savings\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Quiet operation</li>\r\n 	<li>80% AFUE means the unit can significantly reduce your heating costs, when compared to an older furnace.</li>\r\n 	<li>Great savings - Save energy and save money on your monthly bills</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Lennox Elite Series, TWO-STAGE GAS FURNACE', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lennox-furnace-3', '', '', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=312', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(314, 1, '2020-07-17 04:40:48', '2020-07-17 04:40:48', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Maintains perfect temperature</li>\r\n 	<li>Uses up to 70% less energy</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic error-monitoring system</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Samsung Smart Whisper Heat Pump', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'samsung-smart-whisper-heat-pump', '', '', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=314', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(315, 1, '2020-07-17 04:42:05', '2020-07-17 04:42:05', 'If youre looking for a high-efficiency way to cool down for this summer and many more to come, the Lennox 13ACX boasts an efficiency rating that meets or exceeds 13 SEER.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Durable heavy-gauge, galvanized steel PermaGuard cabinet to resist the elements for years to come</li>\r\n 	<li>High-efficiency outdoor coil provides exceptional heat transfer and low air resistance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple SEERs', 'Lennox Air Conditioner', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lennox-seer-air-conditioners', '', '', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '2021-03-25 22:04:49', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=315', 0, 'products', '', 0);
