3e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2017\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-244\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-HCSI-300x104.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022211\\u0022 height=\\u002273\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eLaunched joint venture between SGHS \\u0026amp; Home Corp Services Inc creating HCSI Home Comfort Inc to focus on residential new construction builders in the GTA.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eAcquired Green Planet Home Services (\\u0022GP\\u0022) with 1,700 accounts, Ontario Consumers Home Services (\\u0022OCHS\\u0022) and Simply Comfort Home Services (\\u0022SCHS\\u0022) with ~53,000 accounts\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2018\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eAwarded Top 15 Great Places to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2019\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eAwarded Top 4 Great Places to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2020\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-251\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-simply-retail-300x139.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022164\\u0022 height=\\u002276\\u0022 /\\u003e \\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-245\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-home-depot-300x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u002272\\u0022 height=\\u002272\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eLaunched Simply Green Retail Services with Home Depot\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eNamed Best Business of the Year (+100 employees) by the CanadianSME National Business Awards\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWere proud to have been ranked as Great Place To Work, 5 years in a row.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-240\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-CanadianSME-Award-300x125.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022209\\u0022 height=\\u002287\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green has been named Best Business of the Year (+100 employees)\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThis honour was announced at an event hosted by CanadianSME Business Magazine in partnership with Cisco, Lenovo, and RBC, and is recognition of Simply Greens rapid assent to the ranks of Canadas most successful and leading companies.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":240,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 400px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-url\":\"/press-release/simply-green-has-been-named-best-business-of-the-year-100-employees/\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces in Canada\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eSimply Green Home Services Inc., one of Canada\'s leading industry specialists in energy efficient home comfort solutions, is proud to announce that it has been recognized as the 4th best place to work in Canada by Great Place to Work in the less-than-100-employees category. \\u0022We are deeply honoured to be recognized as one of the top five Best Workplaces in Canada this year,\\u0022 said Lawrence Krimker, CEO, Simply Group and Simply Green Home Services.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":243,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 250px;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/press_release/simply-green-recognized-as-one-of-the-best-workplaces-in-canada/\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green Home Services To Make Friendly, Premium All-Cash Offer to Acquire Dealnet\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eSimply Green has invested strategically to become a leader in the home comfort and home energy solutions sector, and this deal represents the next step in our continued growth. We are pleased this transaction will be adding over $200 million of finance receivables to our growing business, said Lawrence Krimker, Chief Executive Officer of Simply Group. With Simply Greens expansive and growing product offerings, and Dealnets underlying strength, we believe this acquisition will benefit our customers and investors and positions us well for the future. We look forward to commencing the tender process as soon as possible.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":500,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 250px;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/08/24/2082594/0/en/Simply-Green-Home-Services-To-Make-Friendly-Premium-All-Cash-Offer-to-Acquire-Dealnet.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Investors', '', 'inherit', 'clo