 the pandemic. VersaBanks Point-of-Sale Financing business has been the primary driver of the significant expansion of our lending portfolio for the last eight years and we see this partnership as a tremendous opportunity for both organizations to execute on their growth strategies.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":735,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-snap-financial-group-in-a-transaction-valued-at-511-million-885985213.html\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green Home Services To Make Friendly, Premium All-Cash Offer to Acquire Dealnet\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022Simply Green has invested strategically to become a leader in the home comfort and home energy solutions sector, and this deal represents the next step in our continued growth. We are pleased this transaction will be adding over $200 million of finance receivables to our growing business, said Lawrence Krimker, Chief Executive Officer of Simply Group. With Simply Greens expansive and growing product offerings, and Dealnets underlying strength, we believe this acquisition will benefit our customers and investors and positions us well for the future. We look forward to commencing the tender process as soon as possible.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":737,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/08/24/2082594/0/en/Simply-Green-Home-Services-To-Make-Friendly-Premium-All-Cash-Offer-to-Acquire-Dealnet.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Investors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '156-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-14 14:11:50', '2020-10-14 14:11:50', '', 156, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/156-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
