(784, 2, '2020-10-23 16:27:44', '2020-10-23 16:27:44', 'Simply Green Home Services has been ranked in the Best Place to Work list for the fifth straight year in 2020. Significantly, this is our first-year ranking in the new 100-999 employee category, where we ranked 37th across all of Canada. We are proud to be recognized for our amazing culture, mainly because this recognition is based on feedback from our employees! We work tirelessly to develop programs and growth opportunities for our team. This achievement is proof that as we continue to grow and prosper, we continue to maintain and foster the family-style qualities that have made this such a great place to work.\n\nOur employees have always been our biggest asset, so providing them with a positive, inclusive, fun and rewarding work environment is a priority for us. Each year, we strive to build a company culture that empowers and inspires performance. Our goal is to deliver the best possible employee experience, and, to make that happen, we are continuously looking for ways to raise the bar, said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of Simply Group.\n\nAbout Simply Green Home Services\nSimply Green is one of Canadas leading residential and commercial energy services companies, with over 150 team-members and licensed contractors delivering energy-efficient solutions to over 160,000 happy clients across Canada. Simply Green was founded on the core premise of helping Canadians increase their homes energy efficiency without sacrificing their quality of life, resulting in reduced energy consumption, cost savings and an improved home environment.\n\nAbout Great Place to Work: Great Place to Work (www.greatplacetowork.ca) is the global authority on high-trust, high-performance workplace cultures. Through proprietary assessment tools, advisory services, and certification programs, Great Place to Work recognizes the Best Workplaces across the world in a series of national lists, including those published by Fortune magazine (USA) and The Globe &amp; Mail (Canada). Great Place to Work provides the benchmarks, framework, and expertise needed to create, sustain, and recognize outstanding workplace cultures.', 'Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces in Canada', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '268-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-10-23 16:27:44', '2020-10-23 16:27:44', '', 268, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/268-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
