(1072, 2, '2021-01-18 20:50:15', '2021-01-18 20:50:15', '<!-- wp:block-lab/sg-hero {\"title\":\"We\'re Simply Green\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWere in the business of making you and your family more comfortable.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/contact-us#contact-form\",\"link-text\":\"We\'re here to help\",\"link-style\":\"button\"},{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Call Us\",\"link-url\":\"tel:18007645138\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]},\"image-side\":1063,\"image-position\":\"center\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Best in the Business\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eOur goal is to make your home more energy-efficient and environmentally friendly.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe were founded on the simple premise of improving your overall comfort and quality of life. Youve got access to the best and brightest minds in the HVAC industry. Our technical and service professionals are all certified, licensed, and provide unparalleled service and support. They can handle any job  big or small.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1055,\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Happy Employees Happy Results\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWe could tell you that Simply Green employees love the work they do for our customers, but the fact that theyve voted us as a Great Place to Work  for the sixth consecutive year  speaks for itself! This country-wide certification  conducted independently by Great Place to Work Institute Canada  is based on direct, thorough and anonymous feedback from employees about their workplace experience. Weve come a long way as a Great Place to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1056,\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"/careers/\",\"link-text\":\"Learn More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"},{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Call Us\",\"link-url\":\"tel:18007645138\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'clos